        <detaileddescription>
<para>Starts a span.</para>
<para>Optionally sets attributes at <ref refid="classopentelemetry_1_1trace_1_1Span" kindref="compound">Span</ref> creation from the given key/value pairs.</para>
<para>Attributes will be processed in order, previous attributes with the same key will be overwritten.</para>
<para>Note: Adding attributes and links at span creation is preferred to adding them later, as samplers can only consider information already present during span creation. </para>
        </detaileddescription>
